/section><section class="venue-grid" id="venueGrid"></section><section class="why-section"><div class="section-head"><div><div class="section-kicker">Why WTW Indulge</div><h2 class="section-title">Where Great Nights Begin</h2></div><p class="section-note">A selective dining and lounge request layer for guests who care where the night begins.</p></div><div class="why-grid"><div class="why-card"><div class="why-num">01</div><h3>Curated before the night starts</h3><p>Dinner rooms, rooftops, lounges, and celebration tables are selected for atmosphere, timing, and fit.</p></div><div class="why-card"><div class="why-num">02</div><h3>WTW Concierge Review</h3><p>WTW reviews party size, timing, occasion, and room fit before routing the request for confirmation.</p></div><div class="why-card"><div class="why-num">03</div><h3>Dining and nightlife intelligence</h3><p>Built to support partner confirmations, member preferences, city drops, and future concierge routing.</p></div></div></section></div></main><div class="request-modal" id="requestModal" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeReservation()"><div class="request-sheet"><div class="request-head"><div><h2>Request a Reservation</h2><p id="requestContext">WTW Concierge Review for New York. Access subject to partner confirmation.</p></div><button class="close-btn" onclick="closeReservation()" aria-label="Close reservation request">×</button></div><div class="reservation-preview" id="reservationVenuePreview"></div><div class="concierge-steps"><div><strong>WTW reviews request</strong></div><span>&darr;</span><div><strong>Partner receives request</strong></div><span>&darr;</span><div><strong>Confirmation returned</strong></div></div><form class="request-form" id="requestForm"><div class="field"><label for="guestName">Name</label><input id="guestName" name="guestName" autocomplete="name" required></div><div class="field"><label for="guestContact">Phone or email</label><input id="guestContact" name="guestContact" required></div><d